title: Ultrastar.Singstar.ABBA.2008-DJPO (includes videos)
description:
Ultrastar Deluxe is the PC version of PS2/3 Karaoke game. For more information and dowloading this free game, pl go to http://www.ultrastardeluxe.org 

Just place the "Singstar" folder into your Ultrastar songs folder and you're ready to go.

This pack includes the songs from Singstar ABBA including the videos.
